---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Watch — Alisia Martinez" description="Stories, build logs, and mini-doc energy.">
  <section class="space-y-10">
    <header class="space-y-4">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <h1 class="h1">Watch ✦</h1>
        <img src="/doodles/sparkle.svg" alt="" class="mt-2 h-7 w-7" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg muted max-w-3xl">
        Stories, build logs, and mini-documentary energy—coming together piece by piece.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="card p-8 space-y-4">
      <div class="label">What I’m making</div>
      <ul class="muted list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Build logs:</strong> how I prototype and iterate</li>
        <li><strong>Docs & essays:</strong> story-led breakdowns of creative/technical projects</li>
        <li><strong>Behind the scenes:</strong> tools, decisions, and “what I learned”</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="muted">
        A short trailer will live here soon—something that sets the tone and makes the channel feel real.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="line my-10" />

    {/* Optional “series” blocks */}
    <section class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <div class="card p-6 space-y-2">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Docs & Essays</div>
        <div class="muted text-sm">Narrative breakdowns with a serious + playful tone.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6 space-y-2">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Build Logs</div>
        <div class="muted text-sm">From idea → prototype → iteration, with receipts.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6 space-y-2">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold">Behind the Scenes</div>
        <div class="muted text-sm">Process, tools, and the messy middle.</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card p-8 space-y-4">
      <div class="label">Want updates?</div>
      <p class="muted">
        If you want the channel link when the first video is live, send me a note.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-3">
        <a class="btn" href="/contact">Contact</a>
        <a class="btnGhost" href="/work">Browse work</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>